{"tid":1830000,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家入嚟聽我講一句，警察仲信得過","createTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T10:51:35.000Z","uid":57220,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c3d1af2a433b0ea6e8759b7e7382e45c7a29c3","tid":1830000,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"身邊有唔少白警，因為呢場運動而調職<br />\n幫人搵吓失物，做返守護市民既好警察<br />\n想大家明白唔係警察都有好人"},{"pid":"f5f2146eab5facb69db89a84f138043b65e4ce2f","tid":1830000,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">「分化撚」勇武又分，廣告界擺工又分，理大又分。希望大家係檢討而唔係指責</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#57220 - 蕉皮</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>屠龍小隊原來有槍 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>不過冇開過<br />\n龍鳩毛都未跌一條就柒左</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1775037/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實勇武出黎做乜柒？識反省未 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>一個二個爭住出黎柒<br />\n今日係和平示威又掉哂戲油彈 <br />\n有咩作用先？你話你行出黎 一個頂十個就話<br />\n又唔係 剩係識鳩黎唔用腦<br />\n又唔聽人勸<br />\n鳩鳩下 仆街</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1774539/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請全部手足聽住 如果唔係廣告界既罷工 香港唔會走到呢一步 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>搞到香港鬼死咁亂 都不突止<br />\n仲要掉器油彈 諗住過左區選就肯收手<br />\n點知<br />\n又搞個廣告班鬼頭仔搞罷工 搞死香港<br />\n希望大家咪再同佢地癲 <br />\n感謝！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1772605/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>理工班人係咪戇鳩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>磨爛蓆，一早出黎就唔撚死咁多手足啦<br />\n睇班柒頭個樣又唔似做勇武<br />\n和理非香港人大撚把啦 洗撚十換一你咩<br />\n話比你班理工戇鳩仔知，你地直接殺死成班手足<br />\n千古罪人呀</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1739535/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日去出元朗班傻閪死哂未？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>又要撩班黑社會<br />\n又唔敢出去（得幾百人）<br />\n比人打又嗌生嗌死十足廢柴mk係到叫囂<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhehe.gif&h=ad0bad84&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1373507/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"2ad07ceddab6abd143de6d72ae6f7923a5f95ec4","tid":1830000,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d1c3d1af2a433b0ea6e8759b7e7382e45c7a29c3","tid":1830000,"uid":57220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"身邊有唔少白警，因為呢場運動而調職<br />\n幫人搵吓失物，做返守護市民既好警察<br />\n想大家明白唔係警察都有好人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"*明白警察都有好人"},{"pid":"4ea1755a9e274af6e9ef3efec306761974ae4bb0","tid":1830000,"uid":177213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdWvnDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgdWvnDh.png&h=1e53df12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22d56636e24a59e63fff9b78dfd19ae585404dfe","tid":1830000,"uid":158513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"拉"},